article.headline: UT-Martin 48, Murray St. 26
article.story: MARTIN, Tenn. -- Jason McNair rushed for 104 yards and three touchdowns and Tevi Barksdale added two scores on 118 yards to lead Tennessee-Martin to a 48-26 victory over Murray State on Thursday night. The Skyhawks (2-1, 1-1 Ohio Valley) went ahead 28-0 in the first quarter on three McNair touchdowns to put the game away. Derek Carr was 20-for-33 with 255 yards passing and one touchdown. Casey Brockman was 27-for-38 in the air with one touchdown for the Racers (2-2, 1-1). Mike Harris added a score on 121 yards on the ground.
